  <purpose>
   <p>
    This part of ISO 10303 specifies the application interpreted construct for the description 
    of structures to associate the annotation used in draughting with the geometric aspects 
    of the shape where the annotation applies.
   </p>
	<p>
		Technical modifications to the first edition of this part of ISO 10303 are categorised as follows: changes to the EXPRESS
		declarations, new EXPRESS declarations, and changes to definitions of EXPRESS entity data types.
	</p>
