<schema name="aic_associative_draughting_elements" version="3" number="9671" number.supersedes="8489">
<!-- Note schema EXPRESS are in ..\resources\resource_name name_of_schema.xml -->
   
   <introduction>
   		This application interpreted construct provides a consistent set of entities for the
        description of structures to associate the annotation used in draughting 
        with the geometric aspects of the shape where the annotation applies.
   </introduction>
  
   <fund_cons>
   <p>The following entities are intended to be independently instantiated in the application protocol schemas that use this AIC:</p>
   <ul>
	   <li>annotation_curve_occurrence;</li>
	   <li>annotation_fill_area_occurrence;</li>
	   <li>annotation_occurrence_associativity;</li>
	   <li>annotation_symbol_occurrence;</li>
	   <li>dimension_text_associativity;</li>
	   <li>draughting_callout;</li>
	   <li>leader_curve;</li>
	   <li>projection_curve;</li>
	   <li>shape_aspect_associativity;</li>
	   <li>shape_definition_representation;</li>
	   <li>shape_dimension_representation.</li>
   </ul>
   </fund_cons> 
   
